#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:538
msgid "This screen provides the basic settings for configuring AutoClose."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:539
msgid "Enable the scheduler option to autoclose comments and/or pingbacks/trackbacks as per the options set in the Comments and Pingbacks/Trackbacks tabs."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:544
msgid "This screen provides settings to automatically close comments."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:545
msgid "Enable the Close comments option to close comments on posts as per the schedule in the General tab. You can select the post types on which you want to close comments and the age of the post in days."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:546
msgid "If you want to keep comments on certain posts open, enter a comma-separated list of post IDs in the field provided."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:551
